---

<Layout
  seo={seo}
>
  <Container>

	<b>Under re-construction...</b><br>
	Because I let my website fall into the evil claws of Gtranslate(.io) I have to start over. 

    <p>
Meanwhile, feel free to reach out to me:

<!-- h-card -->
    <div id="hcard-mdohr07" class="vcard">

<!--
            <img
                class="u-photo"
                src="https://mdohr.space/mblip-full.png"
                alt="mdohr07"
                width="200"
            /> -->
 

            <p>
                URL: <a class="u-url u-uid" rel="me" href="https://mdohr.space"
                    >https://mdohr.space</a
                ><br />
                Email: <a class="email" href="mailto:mdohr07@gmail.com"
                    >mdohr07(at)gmail.com</a
                >
            </p>

            <p>
                <img
                    src="/assets/icons/mastodon.png"
                    alt="mastodon pixel icon"
                    class="icons"
                />
